properties.Name: ClaimDateType
properties.Description:
The type of date.

Dates related to a Claim can include:

Ex:
- Filed date
- Death Certificate Certified Date
- Received date
- Adjusted date
- Examiner Authorization Of Payment Date
- Paid date
- Arbitration requested date
- Arbitration completed date
- Claim paid date
- Claim denied date

Dates associated with an Insurance Policy can include:

Ex:
- Effective Date
- Expiration Date
- Exclusions Change Date
- Binder Change Date
- Non-Renewal Date
- Cancellation Date

Columns.Name: ClaimDateTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Claim Date Type.

Columns.Name: ClaimDateTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of the Claim Date Type.

Columns.Name: ClaimDateTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of the Claim Date Type.
